{"article_id":"65WJ7Bkecevzx5MZ","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Donald Trump has declared a national emergency at the southern border in an attempt","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"to get his border wall built .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"It ' s a move","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"he ' s been teasing for weeks .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"\" We ' re going to be signing today","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"and registering national emergency ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"and it ' s a great thing","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"to do , \"","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"Trump said in a speech at the White House Rose Garden on Friday","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"announcing the decision .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"He claimed","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"the measure was needed","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"to stop an \" invasion \" of people , gangs , and drugs .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"( There is no such invasion . )","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"Trump is simultaneously signing a bill","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"to fund the government through September","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"and taking executive action ,","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"including declaring a national emergency at the US-Mexico border .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"In December , he refused to sign a funding bill ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"spurring a 35-day partial government shutdown .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"The funding bill","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"he will now sign","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"actually has less money for physical barriers than a bipartisan bill","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"the Senate had proposed last year .","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"As ' s Li Zhou explains ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"this legislation has $ 1.375 billion for \" existing technologies , \" such as the current fencing at the southern border .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"The Senate ' s prior legislation had $ 1.6 billion .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"Trump wanted $ 5.7 billion for the construction of some 200 miles of wall .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"He is now declaring a national emergency in addition to the spending deal","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"because he doesn ' t want it to look like he lost .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"But can he do it ?","depth":4},{"id":31,"text":"Many Democrats and some legal scholars have said","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"that Trump can ' t declare a national emergency","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"to get the border wall funded .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"Others say","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"there are avenues","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"he could definitely try ,","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"setting up potential battles in Congress and in the courts .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"\" He has broad leeway","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"to declare an emergency , frankly ,","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"whether one exists or not , \"","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"Elizabeth Goitein , a co-director of the Liberty and National Security Program at the Brennan Center for Justice ,","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"who recently wrote an in-depth explainer of presidential emergency powers in the Atlantic ,","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"told me in January .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"Trump invoking emergency powers is indicative of how far he ' ll go","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"to appease his base -","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"Trump is so hell-bent on his wall ,","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"it seems he ' ll try almost anything .","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"Or at least to continue with this political stunt .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"\" This is really kind of Hollywood-like , what he ' s trying to do , \"","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"Princeton University political historian Julian Zelizer said .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"How Trump thinks","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"he could get the wall","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"by declaring a national emergency","depth":4},{"id":54,"text":"Many presidents have declared national emergencies ,","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"including George W. Bush after 9/11 and Barack Obama during the swine flu outbreak in 2009 .","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"In recent history , they ' ve done so under the National Emergencies Act of 1976 ,","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"which lets presidents issue an emergency declaration","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"but under certain constraints","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"- namely , Trump can only use specific powers","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"Congress has already codified by law ,","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"and he has to say which powers he ' s using .","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"The 1976 law was actually passed","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"to rein in presidential power","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"and codify how presidents were going about declaring emergencies , from Franklin D. Roosevelt to Richard Nixon .","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"It offers no definition for what counts as an emergency .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"In trying to get wall funding through the National Emergencies Act ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"the question then becomes which existing laws he can try to use","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"to get the money .","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"That ' s where he","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"- and the legal scholars","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"trying to figure out what he ' s talking about -","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"run into trouble :","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"identifying the laws and statutes","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"he could actually use .","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"The Brennan Center for Justice tracks about 130 laws","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"that contain special powers","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"Trump could access .","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"\" It could be that","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"by putting together a lot of different sources of emergency authority ,","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"the president could tap a lot of different funds","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"and at least start , \"","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"Kim Lane Scheppele , a professor at the Center for Human Values at Princeton University , told me .","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"She pointed to a handful of preexisting laws","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"the president could potentially use .","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"He could , for example , reallocate military spending on construction projects for the wall .","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"One law allows the defense secretary , after a national emergency declaration , to direct the army ' s civil works program to construct a structure","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"needed for national defense","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"and use the military budget","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"to do it .","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"Another lets the secretary direct other military services for construction projects .","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"For example , money could come out of the budget","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"for building housing on military bases for service members and into the budget for the wall .","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"Or Trump could declare a \" state of immigration emergency , \"","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"which unlocks an immigration emergency fund .","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"It ' s generally supposed to be used","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"to help states feed and house migrants","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"and process their claims ,","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"but Scheppele said","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"that it is \" vaguely worded enough","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"to permit an edgy interpretation \"","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"that could get the funds for the wall .","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"The issue there is that the fund only has about $ 20 million at the moment , not enough for Trump ' s wall .","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"The White House on Friday identified a couple of specific options for Trump","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"to try to cobble together funds .","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"Ahead of the announcement on Friday , officials said","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"he would redirect about $ 600 million from the Treasury Forfeiture Fund , an account","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"funded by money","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"seized by the US government ;","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"$ 2.5 billion from the Department of Defense ' s counter-drug activities ; and $ 3.6 billion from other military construction accounts .","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"Trump won ' t try to take anything from disaster relief .","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"Since Trump started talking about declaring an emergency","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"to fund the border wall ,","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"there has been some debate","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"about whether he has the legal authority","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"to do so .","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"Bruce Ackerman , a law professor at Yale University , wrote in an op-ed for the New York Times","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"that Trump can not declare an emergency at the border ,","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"arguing","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"that Trump ' s actions would be illegal ,","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"and they would force the armed forces","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"tasked with carrying out his orders","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"to choose between abiding by the commander-in-chief ' s wishes","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"and committing a federal crime .","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"\" The president of the United States has a constitutional duty","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"to take care","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"that the laws be faithfully executed , \"","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"Ackerman said in a subsequent phone interview .","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"\" It is unconstitutional for him to take care to violate the laws of the United States . \"","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"Others have echoed Ackerman ' s declaration","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"that Trump can ' t lawfully declare a state of emergency for the wall .","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"Rep. Adam Schiff","depth":15},{"id":132,"text":"( D-CA )","depth":15},{"id":133,"text":"in an appearance on CNN ' s State of the Union said","depth":14},{"id":134,"text":"the idea was a \" nonstarter. \"","depth":13},{"id":135,"text":"Fox News judicial analyst Andrew Napolitano said in a Fox Business appearance","depth":14},{"id":136,"text":"that the president \" can not spend money","depth":15},{"id":137,"text":"unless it ' s been authorized by Congress . \"","depth":15},{"id":138,"text":"Some have pointed to a Korean War-era court case , Youngstown Sheet & Tube Co. v. Sawyer ,","depth":15},{"id":139,"text":"in which the Supreme Court ruled","depth":16},{"id":140,"text":"that President Harry Truman ' s attempt","depth":18},{"id":141,"text":"to nationalize US steel mills during a strike in the Korean War","depth":18},{"id":142,"text":"was unconstitutional .","depth":17},{"id":143,"text":"\" If Harry Truman couldn ' t nationalize the steel industry during wartime ,","depth":16},{"id":144,"text":"this president doesn ' t have the power","depth":17},{"id":145,"text":"to declare an emergency","depth":18},{"id":146,"text":"and build a multibillion-dollar wall on the border , \"","depth":18},{"id":147,"text":"Schiff told CNN .","depth":15},{"id":148,"text":"Scheppele , however , expressed skepticism","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"that the case actually applies in what Trump is proposing to do .","depth":13},{"id":150,"text":"\" Once you get into the specific area of emergency powers ,","depth":14},{"id":151,"text":"then the president is acting within a delegated framework , \"","depth":14},{"id":152,"text":"she said .","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"Others say","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"Trump can do it","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"- and it might be harder to stop him","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"than you ' d think","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"If Trump does declare a national emergency for the border wall ,","depth":13},{"id":158,"text":"there will almost certainly be challenges to him in both Congress and the courts .","depth":13},{"id":159,"text":"But it ' s not entirely obvious","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"they will stick .","depth":13},{"id":161,"text":"As we saw with Trump ' s travel ban ,","depth":12},{"id":162,"text":"he ' s often willing to do things","depth":14},{"id":163,"text":"that go over the legal line ,","depth":14},{"id":164,"text":"and then leave the courts to figure out where exactly that line lies .","depth":13},{"id":165,"text":"The National Emergencies Act contains a mechanism","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"for Congress to overrule the president","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"by passing a joint resolution out of the House and Senate .","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"With Democrats in control of the House , it would presumably pass there easily ,","depth":13},{"id":169,"text":"and Ackerman , the Yale professor , says","depth":14},{"id":170,"text":"he believes","depth":15},{"id":171,"text":"it could pass the Senate too .","depth":15},{"id":172,"text":"\" Mitch McConnell does not have the power","depth":15},{"id":173,"text":"to bottle this up , \"","depth":15},{"id":174,"text":"he said .","depth":14},{"id":175,"text":"\" So that means that there would be a moment of truth for the Republican Party . \"","depth":13},{"id":176,"text":"But due to a 35-year-old court case , Congress might not be able to override the president that easily .","depth":11},{"id":177,"text":"In the 1983 case Immigration and Naturalization Service v. Chadha , the Supreme Court decided","depth":13},{"id":178,"text":"that a one-house legislative veto violated the Constitution .","depth":13},{"id":179,"text":"After that , the National Emergencies Act was amended","depth":14},{"id":180,"text":"to require the joint resolution","depth":15},{"id":181,"text":"to override the president ' s declaration","depth":15},{"id":182,"text":"- like a typical law , it requires a simple majority in the House and Senate and the president ' s signature .","depth":13},{"id":183,"text":"Trump would probably not be willing to sign a joint resolution","depth":13},{"id":184,"text":"to reject his own emergency declaration ,","depth":13},{"id":185,"text":"so that means","depth":13},{"id":186,"text":"that Congress would need to override him with a two-thirds majority in each chamber .","depth":13},{"id":187,"text":"\" The safeguard","depth":14},{"id":188,"text":"you think","depth":15},{"id":189,"text":"is there in the National Emergencies Act","depth":15},{"id":190,"text":"turns out not to be there ,","depth":13},{"id":191,"text":"or at least most constitutional scholars","depth":16},{"id":192,"text":"who have looked at that question closely","depth":16},{"id":193,"text":"think","depth":15},{"id":194,"text":"that the Supreme Court would never go for it ,","depth":15},{"id":195,"text":"especially now that we have a Supreme Court with two new members","depth":16},{"id":196,"text":"who are unusually deferential to executive power , \"","depth":16},{"id":197,"text":"Scheppele said .","depth":13},{"id":198,"text":"\" It could be that actually nobody could tell him no . \"","depth":11},{"id":199,"text":"McConnell ,","depth":12},{"id":200,"text":"speaking on the Senate floor on Thursday ,","depth":12},{"id":201,"text":"said","depth":11},{"id":202,"text":"he supports the president ' s emergency declaration .","depth":10},{"id":203,"text":"House Speaker Nancy Pelosi","depth":12},{"id":204,"text":"( D-CA )","depth":12},{"id":205,"text":"at a press conference on Thursday said","depth":11},{"id":206,"text":"congressional Democrats would review their options","depth":11},{"id":207,"text":"and are \" prepared to respond appropriately \" to Trump ' s declaration .","depth":11},{"id":208,"text":"A national emergency declaration for the border wall would likely face a challenge in the courts .","depth":10},{"id":209,"text":"But it ' s not clear which parties would have standing","depth":12},{"id":210,"text":"to file a lawsuit ,","depth":12},{"id":211,"text":"and moreover , any decisions would take time .","depth":11},{"id":212,"text":"Being the first mover","depth":14},{"id":213,"text":"in declaring the emergency","depth":14},{"id":214,"text":"would give Trump a \" tremendous advantage , \"","depth":13},{"id":215,"text":"Ackerman said .","depth":12},{"id":216,"text":"\" There are good legal challenges ,","depth":13},{"id":217,"text":"to be sure ,","depth":13},{"id":218,"text":"and I think","depth":14},{"id":219,"text":"there would be a real fight , \"","depth":14},{"id":220,"text":"Goitein , from the Brennan Center , said .","depth":13},{"id":221,"text":"Trump on Friday anticipated the court battle .","depth":11},{"id":222,"text":"\" Look , I expect to be sued , \"","depth":12},{"id":223,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":224,"text":"Some Republicans previously encouraged Trump to declare the emergency .","depth":8},{"id":225,"text":"Sen. Lindsey Graham","depth":11},{"id":226,"text":"( R-SC )","depth":11},{"id":227,"text":"in a tweet earlier in January called on the president to declare an emergency","depth":11},{"id":228,"text":"to build the wall .","depth":11},{"id":229,"text":"Rep. Mo Brooks","depth":12},{"id":230,"text":"( R-SC )","depth":12},{"id":231,"text":"said in an interview on CNN","depth":11},{"id":232,"text":"that Trump had the right","depth":12},{"id":233,"text":"to declare an emergency","depth":12},{"id":234,"text":"\" because the United States code says so .","depth":11},{"id":235,"text":"\" Mr. President , the Democrats are not working in good faith with you .","depth":9},{"id":236,"text":"Declare emergency ,","depth":10},{"id":237,"text":"build the wall now .","depth":10},{"id":238,"text":"- Lindsey Graham","depth":10},{"id":239,"text":"( @ LindseyGrahamSC )","depth":10},{"id":240,"text":"January 11 , 2019","depth":9},{"id":241,"text":"Beyond the legal questions around what Trump can do and how he can do it , there are some more fundamental issues :","depth":4},{"id":242,"text":"The US government was shut down over a campaign trail call","depth":6},{"id":243,"text":"that Trump uses","depth":7},{"id":244,"text":"to rile up his base ,","depth":7},{"id":245,"text":"and there ' s no new emergency at the US-Mexico border .","depth":6},{"id":246,"text":"\" There is no national security crisis , \"","depth":8},{"id":247,"text":"Zelizer , from Princeton , said .","depth":8},{"id":248,"text":"\" We are not at war ,","depth":8},{"id":249,"text":"and it ' s not clear anything is happening at the border . \"","depth":8},{"id":250,"text":"This isn ' t the first time","depth":8},{"id":251,"text":"Trump has invented an immigration crisis","depth":9},{"id":252,"text":"when convenient -","depth":9},{"id":253,"text":"ahead of the midterms , he started warning about dire threats from a migrant caravan ,","depth":8},{"id":254,"text":"only to more or less drop the issue","depth":9},{"id":255,"text":"once November 6 came","depth":10},{"id":256,"text":"and went .","depth":10},{"id":257,"text":"Now that Congress won ' t agree to his border wall ,","depth":8},{"id":258,"text":"and obviously Mexico isn ' t paying for it ,","depth":8},{"id":259,"text":"he ' s manufacturing panic yet again .","depth":7},{"id":260,"text":"\" There ' s an emergency","depth":9},{"id":261,"text":"whenever it suits his purposes ,","depth":9},{"id":262,"text":"but that ought not to be the test , \"","depth":8},{"id":263,"text":"said Michael Gerhardt , a constitutional scholar at the University of North Carolina ' s School of Law .","depth":7},{"id":264,"text":"This also puts to the test the Republican Party and its willingness","depth":10},{"id":265,"text":"- or , frankly , lack thereof -","depth":10},{"id":266,"text":"to stand up to Trump .","depth":9},{"id":267,"text":"The GOP spent years","depth":10},{"id":268,"text":"complaining about Obama ' s overreach ,","depth":10},{"id":269,"text":"so","depth":10},{"id":270,"text":"now that Trump is making up an emergency","depth":12},{"id":271,"text":"to pay for a border wall","depth":13},{"id":272,"text":"Congress does not want ,","depth":13},{"id":273,"text":"what will they do ?","depth":11},{"id":274,"text":"\" If this were a Democratic president ,","depth":10},{"id":275,"text":"Republicans would say","depth":11},{"id":276,"text":"Obama is going to have to put up","depth":12},{"id":277,"text":"or shut up .","depth":12},{"id":278,"text":"But","depth":11},{"id":279,"text":"because it ' s Trump ,","depth":12},{"id":280,"text":"Republicans will argue","depth":13},{"id":281,"text":"that we should defer to the president , \"","depth":13},{"id":282,"text":"Gerhardt said .","depth":10},{"id":283,"text":"\" We have to consider at what point this deferral means","depth":9},{"id":284,"text":"the president is usurping legislative authority . \"","depth":9},{"id":285,"text":"Republicans have expressed concern","depth":8},{"id":286,"text":"that Trump ' s emergency declaration now might lead to declarations from future Democratic presidents in the future on issues such as climate change or health care .","depth":8},{"id":287,"text":"Pelosi on Thursday made sure to point that out .","depth":7},{"id":288,"text":"\" I know","depth":9},{"id":289,"text":"the Republicans have some unease about it ,","depth":9},{"id":290,"text":"no matter what they say ,","depth":8},{"id":291,"text":"because","depth":9},{"id":292,"text":"if the president can declare an emergency on something","depth":11},{"id":293,"text":"that he has created as an emergency ,","depth":11},{"id":294,"text":"an illusion","depth":12},{"id":295,"text":"that he wants to convey ,","depth":12},{"id":296,"text":"just think of what a president with values can present to the American people , \"","depth":11},{"id":297,"text":"she said .","depth":8},{"id":298,"text":"Regardless of the concerns , Trump appears determined to give it a go .","depth":7},{"id":299,"text":"\" It ' s certainly not a slam-dunk","depth":10},{"id":300,"text":"that he can , \"","depth":10},{"id":301,"text":"Goitein said ,","depth":9},{"id":302,"text":"\" but it ' s not a slam-dunk that he can ' t , either . \"","depth":8},{"id":303,"text":"After the government shutdown ended ,","depth":8},{"id":304,"text":"she questioned in a Twitter thread Trump ' s tactic","depth":9},{"id":305,"text":"of threatening to declare an emergency","depth":10},{"id":306,"text":"if Congress doesn ' t give him what he wants .","depth":10},{"id":307,"text":"If he ' s able to wait three weeks ,","depth":10},{"id":308,"text":"and Congress in that time decides against funding against the wall ,","depth":10},{"id":309,"text":"\" declaring an emergency","depth":11},{"id":310,"text":"to build one anyway","depth":11},{"id":311,"text":"is a massive abuse of power","depth":11},{"id":312,"text":"and quite likely a violation of the Constitution . \"","depth":11},{"id":313,"text":"By going in this direction ,","depth":10},{"id":314,"text":"she wrote ,","depth":10},{"id":315,"text":"\" he makes it about 10 times more likely","depth":10},{"id":316,"text":"that lawsuits","depth":12},{"id":317,"text":"challenging the declaration","depth":12},{"id":318,"text":"will succeed . \"","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":637,"left":369,"right":636,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":369,"left":332,"right":368,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":332,"left":322,"right":331,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":322,"left":320,"right":321,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":320,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":321,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":331,"left":327,"right":330,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":327,"left":323,"right":326,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":323,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"}